See https://sdog.jira.com/browse/JSTDEV-1006: when running in an on-demand environment, the link to the license page is correctly hidden in the admin menu, but is still accessible via UPM. The resulting page shows TC's own licensing form. In on demand mode, we never expect a plugin to show its own license form, since subscriptions are handled via MAC. 

